sections.heading: Attachment; county court; procedure
sections.text: Sections 25-1039 to 25-1041 shall apply to actions before county courts.SourceLaws 1875, § 1, p. 44;R.S.1913, § 7771;C.S.1922, § 8715;C.S.1929, § 20-1042;R.S.1943, § 25-1042;Laws 1972, LB 1032, § 126.
